types.section:
{{fr-prep}}

# {{lb|fr|adverbial}} in the [[opinion]] of, [[according]] to
#: {{uxi|fr|de l'avis de tous, {{...}}|everybody agrees that}}
#: {{uxi|fr|De l'avis de certains experts, porter un masque pour se protéger du coronavirus ne sert à rien.|Some experts think that wearing a mask is of no use against COVID.}}
# {{lb|fr|predicative}} of the same opinion as, [[of a mind]] with
#: {{uxi|fr|Je ne suis pas de votre avis.|I don't share your opinion.}}

====Usage notes====
* When used adverbially, this expression cannot take a possessive pronoun as complement: ''**de mon avis, …'', ''**de votre avis, …''; {{m|fr|à mon avis}}, {{m|fr|à ton avis}}, {{m|fr|à votre avis}} are used instead.
* Not to be confused with {{m|fr|de l'aveu de}}.

====Related terms====
* {{l|fr|d'avis}}

====See also====
* {{l|fr|aux yeux de}}
